<div class="title">Controlled Experiment</div>
<div class="substance">Alcohol - Hard & Diazepam (Valium)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Pete&Exact=1">Pete</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Pete. "Controlled Experiment: An Experience with Alcohol - Hard & Diazepam (Valium) (exp11841)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Apr 14, 2006. erowid.org/exp/11841</div>

<br/>



